{"tid":1616921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國男子持刀巴黎警察總部殺4警　當場遭擊斃 (21:51)","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:51:06.000Z","uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e79ade8117f8393839056057dec41efa7b65aa8","tid":1616921,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎一名男子於當地時間今午（3日）1時，持刀在警察總部施襲，刺死4名警員，刀手其後被其他警員當場擊斃。<br />\n當地傳媒報道，施襲者是警察總部內的行政職員，暫未知其行兇動機。法新社引述消息人士稱，事發在大樓內的庭院。警察總部鄰近巴黎聖母院等旅遊景點，為安全起見，事發後警察總部周邊路段封鎖，最近的一個地鐵站也關閉。法國內政部長及巴黎檢察官趕到現場了解。暫未知是否恐怖襲擊，有法國傳媒引述一名警員稱，可能是尋仇。<br />\n法國近年多次發生針對警員的襲擊事件，2017年，一名槍手在巴黎香榭麗舍大道射殺一名警員。<br />\n（路透社／法新社／中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20191003/s00005/1570109971286/男子持刀巴黎警察總部殺4警-當場遭擊斃\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20191003%2Fs00005%2F1570109971286%2F%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E6%AE%BA4%E8%AD%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCElpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=083763e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20191003%2Fs00005%2F1570109971286%2F%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E6%AE%BA4%E8%AD%A6-%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83&h=05573dab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20191003/s00005/1570109971286/男子持刀巴黎警察總部殺4警-當場遭擊斃</a><br />\n<br />\n法國警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但犠牲, 真心唔好學, 唔係反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7c9d2075a99666a4cd2b2117b5ff22fc24bb08","tid":1616921,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":